channel.title: How do i put the objects from a old home to a new home
channel.description: i changed the home place and i teled there but nuthing there how do i get everything there????

item.title: How do i put the objects from a old home to a new home
item.dc:creator: @gamma gamma
item.description:
@gamma wrote:

Search this is client.java

public void NewObjects() {

you will see these, or something similar to it.

makeGlobalObject(3219, [b]9623[/b], [b]4483[/b], -1, 10);

search the coords of where the object at your old home where and change the numbers in bold to the new coords you would like them to be.

Also the “-1” in that would be the direction the object would be facing, so you could change that to -3, -2, -1, 0, 1, 2, & 3
